{"tid":2487092,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"華為：稱自駕技術已優於Tesla","createTime":"2021-04-13T10:06:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T10:47:14.000Z","uid":155674,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"e024acc392c910b25c228101d4ebeb2c0e3753f8","tid":2487092,"uid":155674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T10:06:19.000Z","msg":"小米在日前敲定未來10年投資100億美元進軍電動車產業，華為也急急腳追來。據外媒《彭博》報導，華為將投資10億美元研發自動駕駛和電動車技術，加速與電動車大廠Tesla和新加入者小米競爭。<br />\n<br />\n華為副董事長徐直軍在深圳見分析師時表示， <span class=\"red\">華為的自動駕駛技術在某些領域已經超越了Tesla，例如，汽車可在無需人工干預的情況下行駛超過1,000公里</span>。<br />\n<br />\n研究公司Canalys估計，因消費者對綠色汽車的喜愛和成本下降，僅中國市場今年的電動汽車銷量或能增長50%以上。但是電動車在中國已經是一個十分擁擠的競技場，其參與者有Tesla，本土派新貴蔚來、小鵬和理想，還有眾多車企，例如吉利等。<br />\n<br />\n華為係咪又要to the moon?<br />\n定係要去美國上市, 做中國電動車第四傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db23b89c861036628a27e29ffd5dcc66fb479dfd","tid":2487092,"uid":155674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T10:06:38.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://businessdigest.io/article/%E5%95%86%E6%A5%AD%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/6971/%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E8%BB%8A%E7%86%B1-%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E6%96%A510%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E8%BB%8A%E4%B9%8B%E6%88%B0-%E7%A8%B1%E8%87%AA%E9%A7%95%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E5%B7%B2%E5%84%AA%E6%96%BCtesla?fbclid=IwAR3FNnUnmiVEe0I1xwJdnHNf05jhMUWpBsc-amfN00i3avgpn0b5B5aAe64</code></pre>"},{"pid":"c78ba78cc1bc8c5402f2b9e682d61960a631d98f","tid":2487092,"uid":295230,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T10:07:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"908f9e78056539f74a63659350553866980d7d9d","tid":2487092,"uid":191453,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-0